0.0.1
- Open and save files (if file is already opened or saved, it overwrites)
- Close / Create tabs (right click tabs for more options)
- Hex to RGB converter (highlight a hex value and it will return the rgb equivalent)
- Status strip (visual information about the current document)
- Console strip (used for typing commands, very limited atm)
- Hide anything obstructing the text area (console, menubar etc, possibly single tabs in the future)
- Shows the current language being used (unique to each tab)

0.0.2
- Added sidebar and synced it with open tabs (it shows list of open files)
- Console can now do simple "File menu operations"
- Various interface tweaks
